<h2>Mashed Sweet Potato</h2>

<div>
  <h3>Ingredients</h3>

  <ul>
    <li>Sweet potatoes</li>
    <li>Mango chutney</li>
    <li>A small bunch of fresh coriander</li>
    <li>Soy sauce</li>
    <li>Lemon juice</li>
    <li>Dried chillis</li>
    <li>Sea salt</li>
    <li>Black Pepper</li>
    <li>Extra virgin olive oil</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div>
  <h3>Method</h3>

  <ul>
    <li>Boil potatoes until soft</li>
  </ul>
</div>

Link to this recipe: http://jsrn.net/tablecloth/#misc/mashedsweetpotato